## v1.6.0 (2026-04-28)

**Changed by:** Ecosystem-wide strict audit session (15 HomericIntelligence repos)
**Verification:** verified-local

### What changed
- Added 7 new Failed Attempts entries documenting rate-limit and duplicate issues from large-scale audit
- Added "Ecosystem-Wide Strict Audit Parameters" to Results & Parameters
- Added new "When to Use" trigger conditions for ecosystem-wide audits
- Updated Verified On table

### Why
First time the swarm pattern was applied to a full 15-repo ecosystem audit + mass issue filing. The session surfaced several new failure modes (org monthly limit, findings.json format enforcement, Write-tool blocking in worktrees, parallel filer duplicates) not covered by prior sessions which handled smaller task sets.

