## v1.3.0 (2026-04-25)

**Changed by:** ProjectProteus 43-issue myrmidon swarm session
**Verification:** verified-local

### What changed
- Added 3 new Failed Attempts entries from ProjectProteus swarm (2026-04-25):
  - Agent-added CI job (`typecheck`) breaks subsequent PRs when lockfile is missing (`npm ci` → `npm install` fix required)
  - Auto-merge disabled at repo level blocks wave completion signal; PRs stay open indefinitely
  - Two agents on same file (`dagger/src/index.ts`) cause merge conflicts even when editing different functions
- Added pre-launch bash checks to Phase 3 (User Approval Gate): `autoMergeAllowed`, `.pre-commit-config.yaml`, lockfile presence
- Added 4 new items to L0 Orchestration Checklist (pre-launch group + post-CI-job-add check)
- Added ProjectProteus row to Verified On table
- Bumped version 1.2.0 → 1.3.0; updated date to 2026-04-25

### Why
Live swarm session on ProjectProteus revealed three new failure modes not previously captured:
auto-merge being disabled changed the completion signal pattern, a mid-session CI job addition
with a missing lockfile dependency cascaded failures to all subsequent PRs, and same-file parallel
agents conflicted despite touching different functions.

