Original 6-phase workflow: Exploration → Plan Design → User Approval Gate → Wave Execution →
CI Monitoring + Fix Loop → Knowledge Capture. Session Timeline reference totalled ~1.5-3 hours
for a typical session. Verified on ProjectHephaestus (32 worktrees → 1, 6 PRs created and
merged, 3 skills captured, 2026-04-05).

Phase 6 ended at "All skill PRs merged in ProjectMnemosyne" with no post-merge tracking issue
step. The L0 Orchestration Checklist ended at `[ ] Phase 6: All skill PRs merged in
ProjectMnemosyne`.
